					<div id="elementor-tab-content-7341" class="elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix" data-tab="1" role="region" aria-labelledby="elementor-tab-title-7341"><p>Yes! You can use almond milk, oat milk, or even coconut water as a dairy-free alternative.</p></div>
