													</span>
												<a class="elementor-toggle-title" tabindex="0">How long can I store a dry fruit smoothie?</a>
					</div>

					<div id="elementor-tab-content-7342" class="elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix" data-tab="2" role="region" aria-labelledby="elementor-tab-title-7342"><p>It’s best consumed fresh, but you can store it in an airtight container in the refrigerator for up to 24 hours.</p><h4> </h4></div>
				</div>
							<div class="elementor-toggle-item">
					<div id="elementor-tab-title-7343" class="elementor-tab-title" data-tab="3" role="button" aria-controls="elementor-tab-content-7343" aria-expanded="false">
