												<a class="elementor-toggle-title" tabindex="0">Is a dry fruit smoothie good for weight loss?</a>
					</div>

					<div id="elementor-tab-content-7343" class="elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix" data-tab="3" role="region" aria-labelledby="elementor-tab-title-7343"><p>Yes, when made without added sugar, it can be a healthy and filling meal replacement.</p></div>
				</div>
							<div class="elementor-toggle-item">
					<div id="elementor-tab-title-7344" class="elementor-tab-title" data-tab="4" role="button" aria-controls="elementor-tab-content-7344" aria-expanded="false">
												<span class="elementor-toggle-icon elementor-toggle-icon-left" aria-hidden="true">
